=== Touchpad ===
Enable two-finger scrolling in X:
{{File|/etc/X11/xorg.conf.d/10-synaptics||<pre>
Section "InputClass"
	Identifier "Touchpad"
        Driver "synaptics"
        MatchIsTouchpad "on"
	Option "VertTwoFingerScroll" "true"
        Option "EmulateTwoFingerMinZ" "40"
        Option "EmulateTwoFingerMinW" "5"
EndSection
</pre>}}

=== Keyboard ===
Configuration for the keyboard in X (adjust as required):
{{File|/etc/X11/xorg.conf.d/30-keyboard||<pre>
Section "InputClass"
        Identifier "Keyboard"
	Driver "evdev"
        Option "XkbLayout" "us"
        Option "XkbModel" "asus_laptop"
	Option "XkbRules" "xorg"
        Option "XkbVariant" ",qwerty"
        MatchIsKeyboard "on"
EndSection
</pre>}}
